WEBVTT

00:00:00.080 --> 00:00:02.310
Good morning, family. I'm excited to

00:00:02.320 --> 00:00:04.789
be with you all again today. I have a

00:00:04.799 --> 00:00:06.550
word for you all, but

00:00:06.560 --> 00:00:08.270
these are just conversations

00:00:08.280 --> 00:00:09.830
that I have with the Lord. I'm going to

00:00:09.840 --> 00:00:11.230
get right to it; I don't want to waste

00:00:11.240 --> 00:00:13.709
your time. I'm going to

00:00:13.719 --> 00:00:15.190
talk to you about some things that the

00:00:15.200 --> 00:00:16.510
Lord has talked to me about because I

00:00:16.520 --> 00:00:18.429
was asking the Lord, 'Lord, what do you

00:00:18.439 --> 00:00:20.109
have for your people? What do you want me

00:00:20.119 --> 00:00:22.230
to talk about today with them?'And he

00:00:22.240 --> 00:00:23.550
said, 'Brandon, just tell them what you

00:00:23.560 --> 00:00:26.630
know.'I

00:00:26.640 --> 00:00:28.310
go back and forth with it,

00:00:28.310 --> 00:00:28.320
asking

00:00:28.320 --> 00:00:30.109
what he wants me

00:00:30.119 --> 00:00:32.229
to talk to his people about, and like I

00:00:32.239 --> 00:00:33.470
said, he just said, 'Tell them what you

00:00:33.480 --> 00:00:36.270
know.'Every

00:00:36.280 --> 00:00:39.510
year I've noticed—this is one of

00:00:39.520 --> 00:00:41.990
the conversations I had with

00:00:41.990 --> 00:00:42.000
him—that

00:00:42.000 --> 00:00:44.350
people

00:00:44.360 --> 00:00:47.310
get colds and the flu a lot during the

00:00:47.320 --> 00:00:49.069
winter

00:00:49.079 --> 00:00:51.750
season. Viruses and things like that

00:00:51.750 --> 00:00:51.760
seem

00:00:51.760 --> 00:00:53.830
to be really rampant. I know

00:00:53.840 --> 00:00:55.990
a lot of people are indoors

00:00:55.990 --> 00:00:56.000
during

00:00:56.000 --> 00:00:58.509
that

00:00:58.509 --> 00:00:58.519
timeframe,

00:00:58.519 --> 00:01:00.310
but I was just curious about it,

00:01:00.320 --> 00:01:02.430
asking questions: 'How do you keep

00:01:02.440 --> 00:01:03.990
yourself healthy? How do you keep

00:01:04.000 --> 00:01:06.830
yourself from getting the flu and all

00:01:06.840 --> 00:01:09.270
these other

00:01:09.270 --> 00:01:09.280
things?'He

00:01:09.280 --> 00:01:10.749
told me,

00:01:10.759 --> 00:01:13.710
'Brandon, people are indoors more and

00:01:13.720 --> 00:01:16.190
more, behind

00:01:16.200 --> 00:01:18.149
desk jobs and things like that.

00:01:18.159 --> 00:01:19.830
They're in the house; they're not out

00:01:19.840 --> 00:01:22.429
active in the summer

00:01:22.439 --> 00:01:25.270
getting their D3 levels

00:01:25.270 --> 00:01:25.280
up.'He

00:01:25.280 --> 00:01:27.550
said to me—and this is for me and my

00:01:27.560 --> 00:01:29.950
house; I am not giving medical advice

00:01:29.960 --> 00:01:32.870
here, you need to ask your doctor for

00:01:32.880 --> 00:01:34.830
your health

00:01:34.830 --> 00:01:34.840
because

00:01:34.840 --> 00:01:36.510
everybody's different. Everybody

00:01:36.520 --> 00:01:37.910
has a different blood chemistry

00:01:37.910 --> 00:01:37.920
and

00:01:37.920 --> 00:01:39.870
a different chemistry

00:01:39.880 --> 00:01:41.310
in their body altogether. I'm just

00:01:41.320 --> 00:01:43.550
telling you what he told me to do for my

00:01:43.560 --> 00:01:45.630
family

00:01:45.640 --> 00:01:47.069
so you can pray about it,

00:01:47.079 --> 00:01:49.749
go to your doctor, and ask them what

00:01:49.759 --> 00:01:52.670
you need for your body. Have

00:01:52.680 --> 00:01:55.190
them check your D3 levels. Whenever the

00:01:55.200 --> 00:01:57.910
Lord spoke to me about this, I went

00:01:57.910 --> 00:01:57.920
and

00:01:57.920 --> 00:02:00.950
had my D3 levels checked—my wife,

00:02:00.960 --> 00:02:03.670
all of us—to see where we were because I

00:02:03.680 --> 00:02:05.870
was curious about it. After the

00:02:05.880 --> 00:02:07.910
Lord speaks to you, I follow up and get

00:02:07.920 --> 00:02:09.910
knowledge about what he's talking about

00:02:12.720 --> 00:02:14.350
instead of just

00:02:14.360 --> 00:02:15.990
making sure it's not your

00:02:16.000 --> 00:02:18.270
flesh. We all

00:02:18.280 --> 00:02:20.670
hear in part and see in part, and

00:02:20.680 --> 00:02:23.070
sometimes we can miss it. So

00:02:23.080 --> 00:02:25.430
I go out and I test it, and I say,

00:02:25.440 --> 00:02:27.070
'Lord, I want to make sure I'm

00:02:27.080 --> 00:02:29.350
hearing you

00:02:29.350 --> 00:02:29.360
correctly,'because

00:02:29.360 --> 00:02:31.270
we're all

00:02:31.280 --> 00:02:33.350
human, we're all a work in progress, and

00:02:33.360 --> 00:02:34.830
we're all striving to get better and

00:02:34.840 --> 00:02:36.750
better. I'm not going to say every

00:02:36.760 --> 00:02:39.110
time I hear him that it's always

00:02:39.120 --> 00:02:41.550
God, because I've missed it. I

00:02:41.560 --> 00:02:43.550
just say, 'Lord, we're all

00:02:43.560 --> 00:02:45.110
doing the best we can.'I went

00:02:45.110 --> 00:02:45.120
and tested

00:02:45.120 --> 00:02:47.149
my

00:02:47.159 --> 00:02:49.550
blood levels, and my levels were really,

00:02:49.560 --> 00:02:52.030
really low at the time.

00:02:52.040 --> 00:02:54.070
The doctor said, 'You

00:02:54.080 --> 00:02:57.390
can increase it by taking some

00:02:57.390 --> 00:02:57.400
D3.'Well,

00:02:57.400 --> 00:03:00.670
it went along identically

00:03:00.680 --> 00:03:03.509
with what the Lord said. He told me

00:03:03.519 --> 00:03:06.190
personally for my kids, by the month of

00:03:06.200 --> 00:03:09.270
October every single year, to start

00:03:09.280 --> 00:03:14.509
taking 10,000 IUS of D3 and K2. Now, the

00:03:14.519 --> 00:03:16.869
K2 is just what usually comes with the

00:03:16.879 --> 00:03:19.070
vitamin that's already there. You

00:03:19.080 --> 00:03:21.589
get it at a health food

00:03:21.599 --> 00:03:23.350
store or you can get it on Amazon. There

00:03:23.350 --> 00:03:23.360
are

00:03:23.360 --> 00:03:26.149
a lot of places that sell

00:03:26.149 --> 00:03:26.159
D3/K2

00:03:26.159 --> 00:03:30.229
combo mixes, but we take 10,000

00:03:30.229 --> 00:03:30.239
IUs

00:03:30.239 --> 00:03:35.509
every single day through October,

00:03:35.519 --> 00:03:39.589
November, December, January, and February,

00:03:39.599 --> 00:03:42.030
and we get our levels pretty high. For

00:03:42.030 --> 00:03:42.040
us, that

00:03:42.040 --> 00:03:45.509
is above 60.

00:03:52.959 --> 00:03:55.149
Like I said, you ask the doctor what's

00:03:55.159 --> 00:03:58.110
best for you and your health and go

00:03:58.120 --> 00:03:59.789
with that, but I'm just telling you what

00:03:59.799 --> 00:04:01.429
we do. I've talked to my doctor, and

00:04:01.439 --> 00:04:03.509
the doctor said it was good for us.

00:04:03.519 --> 00:04:07.270
The Lord was

00:04:07.280 --> 00:04:09.710
showing me that this was a big deal

00:04:09.720 --> 00:04:11.789
concerning the flu virus and

00:04:11.789 --> 00:04:11.799
to

00:04:11.799 --> 00:04:14.910
take

00:04:14.920 --> 00:04:16.990
care of your body this way. I'm just

00:04:17.000 --> 00:04:18.590
trying to tell you all little things

00:04:18.600 --> 00:04:20.749
that the Lord has spoken to me about

00:04:20.759 --> 00:04:24.070
along the way. Now, I found a Doctor

00:04:24.080 --> 00:04:26.870
Garland, and I believe he's in

00:04:26.880 --> 00:04:30.390
Colorado Springs. I'll reach out

00:04:30.400 --> 00:04:32.790
to him and ask if he'd like to be

00:04:32.800 --> 00:04:36.150
on our show. He is a naturopathic doctor. He

00:04:36.150 --> 00:04:36.160
is

00:04:36.160 --> 00:04:38.710
not an MD, but he is a

00:04:38.710 --> 00:04:38.720
naturopathic

00:04:38.720 --> 00:04:41.830
doctor, and he talks a lot

00:04:41.840 --> 00:04:44.310
on other shows; I've heard

00:04:44.320 --> 00:04:46.990
him on other YouTube channels. He is

00:04:47.000 --> 00:04:49.670
brilliant; he did a lot of

00:04:49.680 --> 00:04:52.830
medicine overseas—a lot of natural

00:04:52.840 --> 00:04:55.590
stuff from the earth, greens, and

00:04:55.600 --> 00:04:58.189
things like that.

00:04:58.189 --> 00:04:58.199
'AskDrGarland.com'is

00:04:58.199 --> 00:05:00.270
what his

00:05:00.280 --> 00:05:03.390
website was that I remember. I

00:05:03.400 --> 00:05:04.950
used to get his stuff all the time, too.

00:05:04.960 --> 00:05:06.990
He had shark liver oil and all kinds

00:05:07.000 --> 00:05:09.150
of really cool products that he was

00:05:09.150 --> 00:05:09.160
selling

00:05:09.160 --> 00:05:11.270
on there—keeping your

00:05:11.280 --> 00:05:14.469
iodine levels up, good for your thyroid. There

00:05:14.469 --> 00:05:14.479
is

00:05:14.479 --> 00:05:16.670
all kinds of amazing stuff. I'm

00:05:16.680 --> 00:05:18.590
really into health

00:05:18.590 --> 00:05:18.600
and

00:05:18.600 --> 00:05:20.830
things in the earth that the

00:05:20.840 --> 00:05:23.590
Lord has provided for us. He

00:05:23.600 --> 00:05:26.350
gave us all these amazing herbs,

00:05:26.360 --> 00:05:29.189
greens, and grasses

00:05:29.199 --> 00:05:31.990
to help us with our

00:05:32.000 --> 00:05:36.189
bodies. Another thing: I

00:05:36.199 --> 00:05:39.029
have been interceding for this lady. I

00:05:39.039 --> 00:05:41.430
don't know who you are, but if you're

00:05:41.440 --> 00:05:43.189
watching this right now and you've not

00:05:43.199 --> 00:05:46.309
passed on to be with the Lord yet,

00:05:46.319 --> 00:05:48.350
this is

00:05:48.360 --> 00:05:50.110
heavy.

00:05:50.120 --> 00:05:53.550
The Lord was talking to me about the

00:05:53.560 --> 00:05:55.270
Christmas

00:05:55.280 --> 00:05:57.950
season, and

00:05:57.960 --> 00:06:01.350
he said, 'Brandon, I really want my

00:06:01.360 --> 00:06:05.189
people to enjoy this season right now

00:06:05.199 --> 00:06:08.230
with family. There are not very

00:06:08.240 --> 00:06:10.230
many more of them

00:06:10.230 --> 00:06:10.240
left.'He

00:06:10.240 --> 00:06:14.270
said, 'My son

00:06:14.280 --> 00:06:17.270
is coming,'and he was warning me.

00:06:24.479 --> 00:06:29.629
This

00:06:29.629 --> 00:06:29.639
dispensation

00:06:29.639 --> 00:06:33.350
of time is coming to an

00:06:33.360 --> 00:06:36.390
end.

00:06:36.400 --> 00:06:38.990
It was beautiful the

00:06:39.000 --> 00:06:43.430
way he said it because I saw it for a

00:06:43.440 --> 00:06:46.510
glimpse through his eyes—the way he sees

00:06:46.520 --> 00:06:49.469
us during these times with family

00:06:49.479 --> 00:06:51.990
through what we celebrate in America as

00:06:52.000 --> 00:06:54.830
Thanksgiving, the Christmas

00:06:54.830 --> 00:06:54.840
season, and

00:06:54.840 --> 00:06:56.990
the beginning of the New

00:07:05.800 --> 00:07:08.230
Year.

00:07:15.720 --> 00:07:17.950
There is beauty in family time.

00:07:40.759 --> 00:07:42.909
This dispensation of time is coming

00:07:42.919 --> 00:07:43.830
to an

00:07:43.840 --> 00:07:47.550
end,

00:07:47.550 --> 00:07:47.560
and

00:07:47.560 --> 00:07:50.149
we're about to

00:07:50.159 --> 00:07:53.149
enter into the

00:07:53.149 --> 00:07:53.159
thousand-year

00:07:53.159 --> 00:07:55.309
reign. That

00:07:55.309 --> 00:07:55.319
timeframe

00:07:55.319 --> 00:07:57.070
is going to be different than what

00:07:57.080 --> 00:07:59.390
we've ever seen before. It won't be like

00:07:59.400 --> 00:08:02.869
this, so we need to

00:08:02.879 --> 00:08:05.149
embrace life more. He was saying,

00:08:05.159 --> 00:08:07.230
'Brandon, I want you to enjoy life. I want

00:08:07.240 --> 00:08:09.710
you to enjoy your kids

00:08:09.710 --> 00:08:09.720
and

00:08:09.720 --> 00:08:13.749
enjoy family more, to

00:08:13.759 --> 00:08:16.230
embrace it because it's

00:08:16.230 --> 00:08:16.240
beautiful.'All

00:08:16.240 --> 00:08:20.029
of a sudden, I

00:08:20.039 --> 00:08:23.149
was just interceding,

00:08:23.159 --> 00:08:26.110
and I saw this lady. She was laying

00:08:26.120 --> 00:08:29.589
in bed and she was grabbing the side of

00:08:29.599 --> 00:08:30.469
her

00:08:30.479 --> 00:08:34.029
bed, fighting to stay

00:08:34.039 --> 00:08:37.790
alive. She was at the end of her life.

00:08:37.800 --> 00:08:41.550
This woman was probably in her 90s,

00:08:41.560 --> 00:08:46.350
but she regretted every year

00:08:46.350 --> 00:08:46.360
prior—all

00:08:46.360 --> 00:08:50.550
the years

00:08:50.560 --> 00:08:53.030
coming to the end

00:08:53.030 --> 00:08:53.040
in

00:08:53.040 --> 00:08:57.509
total dread, thinking, 'I didn't do what

00:08:57.519 --> 00:09:00.430
I wanted to do. I didn't live the way I

00:09:00.440 --> 00:09:02.870
wanted to live. I wish I could have

00:09:02.880 --> 00:09:05.590
done things differently. I wish I would

00:09:05.600 --> 00:09:08.590
have raised my kids

00:09:08.590 --> 00:09:08.600
differently.'She

00:09:08.600 --> 00:09:11.910
had so many regrets.

00:09:11.920 --> 00:09:14.190
I believe this woman really exists

00:09:14.200 --> 00:09:15.990
because

00:09:16.000 --> 00:09:18.350
she was fighting to stay alive,

00:09:18.360 --> 00:09:21.230
gripping the sides of her sheets

00:09:21.240 --> 00:09:23.190
because her body was trying to slip

00:09:23.200 --> 00:09:25.550
over into eternity, but

00:09:25.560 --> 00:09:27.550
she was fighting it. She did not want to

00:09:27.560 --> 00:09:31.110
die because she didn't have full

00:09:31.120 --> 00:09:33.750
confidence that she was going to make it

00:09:33.760 --> 00:09:36.590
to heaven. She didn't believe that Jesus

00:09:36.600 --> 00:09:38.190
had forgiven

00:09:38.200 --> 00:09:41.030
her when she confessed her sins.

00:09:41.040 --> 00:09:43.110
The Bible says, 'If you confess

00:09:43.120 --> 00:09:45.630
your sins, he is faithful and just to

00:09:45.640 --> 00:09:48.949
forgive you of your sins and

00:09:48.959 --> 00:09:51.790
cleanse you of all

00:09:51.790 --> 00:09:51.800
unrighteousness.'She

00:09:51.800 --> 00:09:54.870
did not have

00:09:54.880 --> 00:09:58.470
total confidence in what she

00:09:58.480 --> 00:10:00.550
had said out of her mouth because of

00:10:00.560 --> 00:10:03.949
how bad her past was. She was at the

00:10:03.959 --> 00:10:06.790
end of her life, clinging to the side of

00:10:06.800 --> 00:10:09.230
a bed, trying to fight death because she

00:10:09.240 --> 00:10:13.389
was so scared

00:10:13.389 --> 00:10:13.399
and

00:10:13.399 --> 00:10:16.590
tormented by

00:10:18.920 --> 00:10:20.350
it.

00:10:23.279 --> 00:10:25.190
She did not have confidence

00:10:25.200 --> 00:10:27.790
that Jesus Christ had forgiven her.

00:10:30.600 --> 00:10:33.550
She wrestled with

00:10:33.560 --> 00:10:35.069
this a lot, and that's why she was

00:10:35.079 --> 00:10:37.470
fighting in that bed.

00:10:37.480 --> 00:10:39.829
The Lord showed me

00:10:39.839 --> 00:10:42.110
her children. She had three beautiful

00:10:42.120 --> 00:10:45.069
children, and she had not raised

00:10:45.079 --> 00:10:48.190
them in a God-fearing home.

00:10:48.200 --> 00:10:50.470
She was worried about leaving this

00:10:50.480 --> 00:10:53.470
earth because she wanted to be a better

00:10:53.480 --> 00:10:57.069
mother to them and show them that Jesus

00:10:57.079 --> 00:10:59.629
is real,

00:10:59.629 --> 00:10:59.639
trying

00:10:59.639 --> 00:11:03.110
to get them out of

00:11:03.120 --> 00:11:05.750
the grasp of hell

00:11:05.760 --> 00:11:09.190
that she raised them in.

00:11:10.200 --> 00:11:13.550
It

00:11:13.560 --> 00:11:15.230
was heartbreaking. As an intercessor, I

00:11:15.240 --> 00:11:17.269
wept over this for two

00:11:17.279 --> 00:11:20.110
days, praying for this woman because I

00:11:20.120 --> 00:11:22.269
could see her in the spirit every time I

00:11:22.279 --> 00:11:24.949
went before the Father, holding

00:11:24.949 --> 00:11:24.959
onto

00:11:24.959 --> 00:11:28.350
sheets. She was dying in bed, fighting

00:11:28.360 --> 00:11:30.230
with everything she could because she

00:11:30.240 --> 00:11:33.350
didn't want to let go.

00:11:36.600 --> 00:11:39.829
It's appointed unto man once to die.

00:11:39.839 --> 00:11:44.230
All of us are going to die. Jesus is

00:11:44.240 --> 00:11:46.910
coming, yes, but there's an elderly

00:11:46.920 --> 00:11:48.670
generation right now...

00:11:48.680 --> 00:11:50.310
we all know

00:11:50.320 --> 00:11:51.990
everybody's appointed to die.

00:11:52.000 --> 00:11:54.269
If Jesus tarries

00:11:54.269 --> 00:11:54.279
and

00:11:54.279 --> 00:11:56.870
doesn't come back in the next 20 or 30

00:11:56.880 --> 00:11:58.629
years,

00:11:58.639 --> 00:12:00.269
there's going to be a lot of people who go

00:12:00.269 --> 00:12:00.279
to

00:12:00.279 --> 00:12:01.790
the

00:12:01.800 --> 00:12:04.030
graveside. But

00:12:04.040 --> 00:12:06.430
there can be an assurance,

00:12:06.440 --> 00:12:09.790
peace, and joy in going home to be

00:12:09.800 --> 00:12:10.509
with

00:12:10.519 --> 00:12:13.230
him. I was sitting right where I'm at

00:12:13.240 --> 00:12:15.710
now, interceding for that

00:12:15.720 --> 00:12:18.670
lady, and

00:12:18.680 --> 00:12:21.790
I dozed off.

00:12:21.800 --> 00:12:25.870
I felt peace as I left

00:12:25.880 --> 00:12:29.350
my body. God gave me a dream where

00:12:29.350 --> 00:12:29.360
I had

00:12:29.360 --> 00:12:33.150
passed away,

00:12:33.160 --> 00:12:37.430
and I felt peace.

00:12:37.440 --> 00:12:40.030
To be absent from the

00:12:40.040 --> 00:12:43.110
body is to be present with the Lord.

00:12:43.120 --> 00:12:46.670
There is no fear in death when you are a

00:12:46.680 --> 00:12:49.269
believer and you have Jesus Christ as

00:12:49.279 --> 00:12:51.990
your Lord and Savior.

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:02.110
I was interceding for

00:13:02.120 --> 00:13:04.790
this woman and the Lord put

00:13:04.790 --> 00:13:04.800
her

00:13:04.800 --> 00:13:05.910
on my

00:13:05.920 --> 00:13:08.550
heart.

00:13:08.560 --> 00:13:11.069
All of a sudden,

00:13:11.079 --> 00:13:12.750
I just dozed

00:13:12.760 --> 00:13:18.150
off and I felt it: death is

00:13:18.160 --> 00:13:21.590
peaceful. I know it was just

00:13:21.600 --> 00:13:23.350
a dream, but I believe my dreams

00:13:23.360 --> 00:13:25.949
are spiritual. I've never

00:13:25.959 --> 00:13:28.430
tasted death,

00:13:30.839 --> 00:13:33.790
but in my spirit, what I felt right

00:13:33.800 --> 00:13:37.670
then was not fearful; there was peace,

00:13:37.680 --> 00:13:41.069
joy, and love.

00:13:41.079 --> 00:13:44.430
If you ponder on

00:13:44.440 --> 00:13:46.509
death a lot, it

00:13:46.509 --> 00:13:46.519
can

00:13:46.519 --> 00:13:49.230
bring some

00:13:49.240 --> 00:13:52.110
fear,

00:13:52.110 --> 00:13:52.120
but

00:13:52.120 --> 00:13:55.150
the Bible

00:13:55.160 --> 00:13:57.829
says there is a generation that will not

00:13:57.839 --> 00:14:00.910
taste death. Jesus told me,

00:14:00.920 --> 00:14:03.749
'Brandon,

00:14:03.759 --> 00:14:05.749
your generation—this generation—you will

00:14:05.749 --> 00:14:05.759
not.'There

00:14:05.759 --> 00:14:09.470
will be a rapture of the

00:14:09.480 --> 00:14:12.550
church, a catching away of

00:14:12.560 --> 00:14:16.310
my people. You are not

00:14:16.320 --> 00:14:17.670
appointed

00:14:17.670 --> 00:14:17.680
unto

00:14:17.680 --> 00:14:20.870
wrath.

00:14:24.920 --> 00:14:28.870
I

00:14:28.880 --> 00:14:31.350
believe with all my heart that Jesus is

00:14:31.360 --> 00:14:34.110
coming soon.

00:14:34.120 --> 00:14:35.990
As the

00:14:36.000 --> 00:14:38.470
world turns every day, there are people

00:14:38.480 --> 00:14:40.790
going into eternity all the time.

00:14:47.320 --> 00:14:49.790
After I saw that woman being so

00:14:49.800 --> 00:14:53.350
tormented by the spirit of death, so

00:14:53.360 --> 00:14:56.350
afraid of the decisions that she made

00:14:56.360 --> 00:14:59.350
for the last

00:14:59.360 --> 00:15:01.189
90 years...

00:15:01.199 --> 00:15:03.230
she looked real

00:15:03.240 --> 00:15:05.389
elderly to

00:15:05.389 --> 00:15:05.399
me, with

00:15:05.399 --> 00:15:07.310
gray hair and

00:15:07.310 --> 00:15:07.320
a

00:15:07.320 --> 00:15:10.310
wrinkly face,

00:15:13.000 --> 00:15:15.949
holding onto that

00:15:15.959 --> 00:15:19.310
bed. Is your heart right with

00:15:19.320 --> 00:15:23.749
Jesus? If you die today, are you going to

00:15:23.749 --> 00:15:23.759
an

00:15:23.759 --> 00:15:25.870
eternity of fire, or are you going to

00:15:25.870 --> 00:15:25.880
an

00:15:25.880 --> 00:15:27.309
eternity of

00:15:27.319 --> 00:15:30.629
paradise? Eternity is

00:15:30.639 --> 00:15:32.790
forever.

00:15:37.000 --> 00:15:39.350
Are you

00:15:39.360 --> 00:15:41.910
really ready? Is this the last Christmas

00:15:41.920 --> 00:15:44.670
season that you're going to

00:15:44.680 --> 00:15:47.189
experience?

00:15:57.120 --> 00:15:59.269
You may wake up

00:15:59.279 --> 00:16:01.670
tomorrow and be with him in

00:16:01.680 --> 00:16:03.910
paradise forever, or you could be in a

00:16:03.920 --> 00:16:05.230
devil's hell

00:16:05.240 --> 00:16:08.749
forever. Hell was

00:16:08.759 --> 00:16:10.590
made for the fallen angels and the

00:16:10.600 --> 00:16:13.189
devil. You choose hell

00:16:14.160 --> 00:16:17.389
by rejecting

00:16:17.399 --> 00:16:20.870
Jesus. Jesus paid the price for you. You

00:16:20.880 --> 00:16:24.030
don't have to die and go to hell. You can

00:16:24.040 --> 00:16:26.069
train up a child in the way he should go,

00:16:26.079 --> 00:16:27.470
and when he gets older, he'll not

00:16:27.480 --> 00:16:29.710
depart from it. I believe if your

00:16:29.720 --> 00:16:31.189
children are wayward,

00:16:31.199 --> 00:16:33.430
God can turn

00:16:33.430 --> 00:16:33.440
them

00:16:33.440 --> 00:16:36.590
around in just a

00:16:36.600 --> 00:16:39.269
moment.

00:16:39.279 --> 00:16:41.710
They can have a dream

00:16:41.710 --> 00:16:41.720
or

00:16:41.720 --> 00:16:44.990
an encounter with an angel.

00:16:50.480 --> 00:16:53.829
He's faithful, and he loves you.

00:16:56.680 --> 00:16:58.509
I really believe with all my heart

00:16:58.519 --> 00:17:01.389
somebody needs to hear this today:

00:17:01.399 --> 00:17:03.710
Jesus loves you and he has a plan

00:17:03.720 --> 00:17:06.470
for your life.

00:17:08.439 --> 00:17:11.029
When I saw that woman tormented, I

00:17:11.039 --> 00:17:12.590
interceded for her, and the

00:17:12.590 --> 00:17:12.600
Lord

00:17:12.600 --> 00:17:15.150
brought it up in my heart: 'This

00:17:15.160 --> 00:17:18.189
dispensation of time is coming to an end.

00:17:18.199 --> 00:17:20.390
The dispensation of grace is coming to

00:17:20.400 --> 00:17:22.590
an end. We're

00:17:22.600 --> 00:17:25.510
getting ready to go into

00:17:25.510 --> 00:17:25.520
the

00:17:25.520 --> 00:17:27.270
tribulation.'There's

00:17:27.270 --> 00:17:27.280
a

00:17:27.280 --> 00:17:29.070
seven-year

00:17:29.070 --> 00:17:29.080
tribulation

00:17:29.080 --> 00:17:31.230
coming, and we're going to step over into

00:17:31.240 --> 00:17:33.549
that soon. It

00:17:33.549 --> 00:17:33.559
is

00:17:33.559 --> 00:17:35.950
hell on earth, but it is not for you.

00:17:38.000 --> 00:17:41.070
I had a neighbor

00:17:41.080 --> 00:17:42.549
named

00:17:42.559 --> 00:17:45.830
Barney. He was an elderly

00:17:45.840 --> 00:17:49.029
gentleman, and he was walking outside.

00:17:49.039 --> 00:17:51.110
The Lord said, 'I want you to go outside

00:17:51.120 --> 00:17:53.270
and ask him if he's

00:17:53.280 --> 00:17:55.390
born again and if he knows

00:17:57.390 --> 00:17:57.400
me.'He

00:17:59.159 --> 00:18:01.110
said, 'Brandon, he doesn't

00:18:01.120 --> 00:18:04.149
know me, and if he dies tonight,

00:18:04.159 --> 00:18:06.270
son, he's going to spend eternity in

00:18:09.190 --> 00:18:09.200
hell.'So

00:18:11.600 --> 00:18:14.909
I went over and said,

00:18:14.919 --> 00:18:17.549
'Barney, I've known you for a long

00:18:25.870 --> 00:18:25.880
time.'I

00:18:35.559 --> 00:18:38.390
said, 'The Lord wants me to

00:18:38.400 --> 00:18:41.549
ask you: do you know Jesus Christ as your

00:18:41.559 --> 00:18:43.669
Lord and personal

00:18:43.669 --> 00:18:43.679
Savior?'He

00:18:43.679 --> 00:18:48.070
said, 'No, I do not.

00:18:48.080 --> 00:18:50.590
Nobody in any church is

00:18:50.600 --> 00:18:52.630
ever going to want a hypocrite

00:18:52.640 --> 00:18:54.430
like me.

00:18:54.440 --> 00:18:57.990
Jesus doesn't want me.'I said, 'Barney,

00:18:58.000 --> 00:18:59.789
Jesus told me to come and talk to

00:18:59.799 --> 00:19:02.909
you and ask you to get born

00:19:02.919 --> 00:19:05.710
again.'He

00:19:05.720 --> 00:19:08.510
said, 'I don't want

00:19:08.510 --> 00:19:08.520
anything

00:19:08.520 --> 00:19:11.510
to do with religion.

00:19:11.520 --> 00:19:14.390
I've lived a

00:19:14.400 --> 00:19:16.870
very ornery life,

00:19:19.360 --> 00:19:21.830
and nobody wants a hypocrite like me in

00:19:21.830 --> 00:19:21.840
church.'I

00:19:21.840 --> 00:19:23.950
just kept pursuing

00:19:23.960 --> 00:19:26.590
him.

00:19:26.600 --> 00:19:28.510
He said, 'I don't want to

00:19:28.520 --> 00:19:30.310
talk about this.'He

00:19:30.310 --> 00:19:30.320
was elderly,

00:19:30.320 --> 00:19:32.549
so I just kind of... his son

00:19:32.549 --> 00:19:32.559
was

00:19:32.559 --> 00:19:34.310
looking at me like, 'Leave my dad

00:19:34.310 --> 00:19:34.320
alone.'I

00:19:34.320 --> 00:19:37.390
said, 'Well, Barney, I'm

00:19:37.400 --> 00:19:39.430
sorry to hear you say that, but I'm going

00:19:39.440 --> 00:19:41.710
to keep praying for

00:19:45.520 --> 00:19:47.990
you.'Three

00:19:51.360 --> 00:19:55.470
weeks later, Barney passed

00:19:55.480 --> 00:19:57.230
away.

00:19:58.919 --> 00:20:01.750
I

00:20:01.760 --> 00:20:04.950
pray that in that

00:20:04.960 --> 00:20:07.950
time he had an opportunity

00:20:10.840 --> 00:20:12.630
to

00:20:15.679 --> 00:20:19.270
reconsider.

00:20:21.280 --> 00:20:26.270
As far as I know, Barney's in

00:20:26.280 --> 00:20:30.710
hell, but just maybe

00:20:30.720 --> 00:20:33.630
he accepted him.

00:20:40.440 --> 00:20:42.630
I'm just

00:20:42.640 --> 00:20:44.630
going to believe the best.

00:20:44.640 --> 00:20:48.029
But from what I saw,

00:20:48.039 --> 00:20:50.390
Barney went to

00:20:50.400 --> 00:20:54.350
hell, and that bothered me a lot. When

00:20:54.360 --> 00:20:56.789
he passed away, his

00:20:56.799 --> 00:21:00.510
wife, Marie...

00:21:00.520 --> 00:21:03.630
I used to witness to

00:21:03.640 --> 00:21:05.669
her a little bit.

00:21:15.310 --> 00:21:15.320
It's

00:21:25.880 --> 00:21:29.269
so

00:21:29.279 --> 00:21:31.870
important that you're a witness to your

00:21:31.880 --> 00:21:34.269
neighbors and that you tell

00:21:34.279 --> 00:21:37.029
them about Jesus.

00:21:43.320 --> 00:21:46.149
None of us are promised tomorrow.

00:21:49.480 --> 00:21:52.590
Have you

00:21:52.600 --> 00:21:56.110
made Jesus your Lord and personal Savior?

00:21:56.120 --> 00:21:59.750
Don't be like Barney and say

00:21:59.760 --> 00:22:01.549
that you don't want a hypocrite

00:22:01.559 --> 00:22:02.310
in

00:22:02.320 --> 00:22:06.390
church. Your past doesn't matter.

00:22:16.880 --> 00:22:20.430
You can confess your sins

00:22:20.440 --> 00:22:22.789
and Jesus will forgive you right where

00:22:22.799 --> 00:22:23.669
you

00:22:23.679 --> 00:22:27.430
are.

00:22:29.840 --> 00:22:31.830
In

00:22:34.159 --> 00:22:36.789
eternity, Jesus will forgive you.

00:22:36.799 --> 00:22:39.549
You need to just

00:22:39.559 --> 00:22:42.590
ask him for forgiveness and forgive

00:22:42.600 --> 00:22:45.909
yourself. The Bible

00:22:45.919 --> 00:22:48.630
says he has a sea of

00:22:48.640 --> 00:22:51.029
forgetfulness; he casts your sins into it

00:22:51.029 --> 00:22:51.039
and remembers them

00:22:51.039 --> 00:22:54.350
no more.

00:22:59.029 --> 00:22:59.039
You've

00:23:03.760 --> 00:23:06.510
got to

00:23:06.520 --> 00:23:08.669
forgive those that have despitefully

00:23:08.679 --> 00:23:11.230
wronged you.

00:23:11.240 --> 00:23:14.149
I

00:23:14.159 --> 00:23:15.750
have

00:23:19.000 --> 00:23:20.870
to do that all the time.

00:23:29.919 --> 00:23:31.669
The devil will try to

00:23:31.679 --> 00:23:32.909
bring it to your mind.

00:23:34.240 --> 00:23:36.430
I had memories about this

00:23:36.440 --> 00:23:38.149
even a couple of days ago,

00:23:38.159 --> 00:23:40.110
and

00:23:40.120 --> 00:23:42.070
I

00:23:42.080 --> 00:23:45.590
said,

00:23:45.600 --> 00:23:50.070
'No, that's under the blood. I

00:23:50.080 --> 00:23:52.990
refuse to be tormented by that

00:23:53.000 --> 00:23:54.870
anymore.'Whenever

00:23:54.880 --> 00:23:57.549
the devil reminds

00:23:57.549 --> 00:23:57.559
you of

00:23:57.559 --> 00:24:00.310
your past,

00:24:00.320 --> 00:24:03.830
you remind him of his future. You

00:24:03.840 --> 00:24:05.350
say, 'Hey, sucker, you're going to burn in

00:24:05.360 --> 00:24:07.669
hell

00:24:12.000 --> 00:24:14.310
forever.'Don't

00:24:19.000 --> 00:24:22.669
be Barney.

00:24:22.669 --> 00:24:22.679
Accept

00:24:22.679 --> 00:24:24.950
Jesus as your Lord and Savior. I

00:24:24.960 --> 00:24:28.430
pray Barney did, but I didn't see

00:24:28.440 --> 00:24:31.310
fruit of it.

00:24:35.039 --> 00:24:37.950
It's time for your salvation,

00:24:37.960 --> 00:24:40.190
your healing,

00:24:40.190 --> 00:24:40.200
and

00:24:40.200 --> 00:24:42.149
your miracle.

00:24:47.600 --> 00:24:50.549
Father, I just thank you

00:24:50.559 --> 00:24:52.750
that every person

00:24:52.760 --> 00:24:55.149
represented here today would

00:24:57.960 --> 00:25:00.430
know you intimately. They have a

00:25:00.440 --> 00:25:03.389
relationship with you

00:25:03.389 --> 00:25:03.399
and

00:25:03.399 --> 00:25:06.549
a knowing that Jesus paid the

00:25:06.559 --> 00:25:09.590
price for their sins. They are healed

00:25:09.600 --> 00:25:12.070
by his stripes and delivered.

00:25:15.360 --> 00:25:18.510
I thank you

00:25:31.399 --> 00:25:33.430
for every single person

00:25:33.440 --> 00:25:35.950
represented here, that they don't have

00:25:35.960 --> 00:25:39.630
to be afraid of

00:25:39.640 --> 00:25:42.029
death. To be

00:25:42.039 --> 00:25:44.070
absent from the body is to be present

00:25:44.080 --> 00:25:46.070
with the Lord.

00:25:52.070 --> 00:25:52.080
I

00:25:58.600 --> 00:26:00.789
pray for a spirit of peace that

00:26:00.799 --> 00:26:03.789
passes all understanding.

00:26:03.799 --> 00:26:07.029
We bind the

00:26:07.039 --> 00:26:09.870
spirit of torment in the name of Jesus.

00:26:15.679 --> 00:26:17.750
I thank you, Lord, that they will not

00:26:17.760 --> 00:26:20.789
be tormented by death

00:26:20.789 --> 00:26:20.799
or

00:26:20.799 --> 00:26:24.789
satanic bondage.

00:26:39.159 --> 00:26:42.990
I

00:26:55.679 --> 00:26:59.310
want you to

00:26:59.320 --> 00:27:01.350
repeat this prayer

00:27:09.120 --> 00:27:11.909
after me: 'Jesus, come into

00:27:11.919 --> 00:27:13.710
my

00:27:13.720 --> 00:27:17.190
heart. Wash me and cleanse me from all my

00:27:17.200 --> 00:27:21.789
sins. Write my name in the Lamb's Book of

00:27:21.799 --> 00:27:25.029
Life. Father, I give my heart to you.

00:27:25.039 --> 00:27:29.350
Jesus, come into me,

00:27:29.360 --> 00:27:32.389
live in me, abide in me. I want to

00:27:32.399 --> 00:27:34.710
make you my Lord and

00:27:34.720 --> 00:27:36.149
personal

00:27:36.159 --> 00:27:39.590
Savior. Jesus, I commit my life to

00:27:59.360 --> 00:28:04.870
you.'For

00:28:19.880 --> 00:28:22.950
God so loved the

00:28:22.960 --> 00:28:24.789
world that he gave his only

00:28:24.799 --> 00:28:26.389
begotten Son, that whosoever

00:28:26.389 --> 00:28:26.399
believes

00:28:26.399 --> 00:28:28.789
in him should not perish but

00:28:28.799 --> 00:28:30.110
have

00:28:30.120 --> 00:28:31.669
everlasting

00:28:31.679 --> 00:28:35.110
life. You've got to believe

00:28:35.120 --> 00:28:38.070
that

00:28:38.080 --> 00:28:40.430
he died for you and rose again

00:28:40.440 --> 00:28:42.669
on the third day.

00:28:42.679 --> 00:28:46.830
It's

00:28:52.399 --> 00:28:54.710
that quick and easy.

00:29:01.080 --> 00:29:03.830
Look at the man on the

00:29:03.840 --> 00:29:06.389
cross. He said,

00:29:06.399 --> 00:29:08.710
'Will you remember

00:29:12.760 --> 00:29:14.870
me?'and

00:29:20.519 --> 00:29:23.669
Jesus said, 'Today you'll be with me in

00:29:40.720 --> 00:29:42.870
paradise.'I

00:30:01.000 --> 00:30:03.190
really appreciate

00:30:03.200 --> 00:30:06.029
you watching. Put a

00:30:06.039 --> 00:30:09.470
thumbs up and click that notification

00:30:09.480 --> 00:30:11.110
bell. It really helps

00:30:11.120 --> 00:30:13.710
get the

00:30:13.720 --> 00:30:17.070
gospel out and

00:30:17.070 --> 00:30:17.080
helps

00:30:17.080 --> 00:30:19.830
people know more about Jesus.

00:30:35.279 --> 00:30:38.870
We're almost to 90,000 subscribers,

00:30:38.880 --> 00:30:42.230
close to 100,000.

00:30:42.240 --> 00:30:44.190
That's my goal

00:30:44.190 --> 00:30:44.200
for

00:30:44.200 --> 00:30:47.870
this year.

00:30:55.760 --> 00:30:58.110
Put a smile on your

00:30:58.120 --> 00:31:00.789
face and a song in your heart. Jesus

00:31:00.799 --> 00:31:03.830
loves you, and we love you. We

00:31:03.840 --> 00:31:06.110
will see you next time.

00:31:06.120 --> 00:31:10.039
Bye-bye.

